---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
const main = "<main>\n\n  <div class=\"hero\">\n    <h1>Health <em>Guides</em></h1>\n    <p>Evidence-based articles on BMI, weight loss, nutrition, and exercise — written to help you understand your health, not just track numbers.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Search box -->\n  <div style=\"max-width:480px;margin:0 auto 24px;padding:0 24px;\">\n    <div style=\"position:relative;\">\n      <input id=\"guide-search\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Search guides… e.g. protein, BMI, sleep\"\n        style=\"width:100%;padding:11px 16px 11px 44px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:100px;font-family:inherit;font-size:.9rem;background:var(--surface);color:var(--ink);outline:none;transition:border-color .2s;\"\n        oninput=\"searchGuides(this.value)\" onfocus=\"this.style.borderColor='var(--accent)'\" onblur=\"this.style.borderColor='var(--border)'\">\n      <span style=\"position:absolute;left:16px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);font-size:1rem;pointer-events:none;\">🔍</span>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Filter tabs -->\n  <div class=\"filters\">\n    <button class=\"filter-btn active\" onclick=\"filterCards('all',this)\" id=\"tab-all\">All <span style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.25);border-radius:100px;padding:1px 7px;font-size:.75rem;margin-left:4px;\">65</span></button>\n    <button class=\"filter-btn\" onclick=\"filterCards('BMI',this)\">BMI <span style=\"background:rgba(45,106,79,0.15);border-radius:100px;padding:1px 7px;font-size:.75rem;margin-left:4px;color:var(--accent);\">14</span></button>\n    <button class=\"filter-btn\" onclick=\"filterCards('Calories',this)\">Calories <span style=\"background:rgba(45,106,79,0.15);border-radius:100px;padding:1px 7px;font-size:.75rem;margin-left:4px;color:var(--accent);\">14</span></button>\n    <button class=\"filter-btn\" onclick=\"filterCards('Nutrition',this)\">Nutrition <span style=\"background:rgba(45,106,79,0.15);border-radius:100px;padding:1px 7px;font-size:.75rem;margin-left:4px;color:var(--accent);\">11</span></button>\n    <button class=\"filter-btn\" onclick=\"filterCards('Exercise',this)\">Exercise <span style=\"background:rgba(45,106,79,0.15);border-radius:100px;padding:1px 7px;font-size:.75rem;margin-left:4px;color:var(--accent);\">7</span></button>\n    <button class=\"filter-btn\" onclick=\"filterCards('Hydration',this)\">Hydration <span style=\"background:rgba(45,106,79,0.15);border-radius:100px;padding:1px 7px;font-size:.75rem;margin-left:4px;color:var(--accent);\">4</span></button>\n    <button class=\"filter-btn\" onclick=\"filterCards('By Height',this)\">By Height <span style=\"background:rgba(45,106,79,0.15);border-radius:100px;padding:1px 7px;font-size:.75rem;margin-left:4px;color:var(--accent);\">8</span></button>\n    <button class=\"filter-btn\" onclick=\"filterCards('By Age',this)\">By Age <span style=\"background:rgba(45,106,79,0.15);border-radius:100px;padding:1px 7px;font-size:.75rem;margin-left:4px;color:var(--accent);\">7</span></button>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- All Guides Grid -->\n  <div class=\"guides-grid\" id=\"guides-grid\">\n\n    <!-- BMI -->\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../what-is-bmi.html\" data-tag=\"BMI\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">📖</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">BMI</div></div></div>\n      <h2>What Is BMI?</h2>\n      <p>A complete explanation of Body Mass Index — how it's calculated, what it measures, and its limitations as a health indicator.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../healthy-bmi-for-women.html\" data-tag=\"BMI\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">👩</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">BMI</div></div></div>\n      <h2>Healthy BMI for Women</h2>\n      <p>What a healthy BMI range looks like for women at different life stages, including pregnancy and menopause considerations.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../normal-bmi-for-men.html\" data-tag=\"BMI\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">👨</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">BMI</div></div></div>\n      <h2>Normal BMI for Men</h2>\n      <p>BMI ranges, body composition differences, and health risk thresholds specific to men across different age groups.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../bmi-chart-by-age.html\" data-tag=\"BMI\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">📈</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">BMI</div></div></div>\n      <h2>BMI Chart by Age</h2>\n      <p>Visual BMI reference charts broken down by age group — see how healthy ranges shift as you get older.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../how-to-lower-bmi.html\" data-tag=\"BMI\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">⬇️</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">BMI</div></div></div>\n      <h2>How to Lower Your BMI</h2>\n      <p>Practical, evidence-based strategies for reducing BMI through sustainable changes to diet, exercise, and lifestyle.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n    <!-- Calories -->\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../how-many-calories-per-day.html\" data-tag=\"Calories\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">🔢</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">Calories</div></div></div>\n      <h2>How Many Calories Per Day?</h2>\n      <p>How to calculate your daily calorie needs based on your age, sex, height, weight, and activity level using validated formulas.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../calories-to-lose-weight.html\" data-tag=\"Calories\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">⚖️</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">Calories</div></div></div>\n      <h2>Calories to Lose Weight</h2>\n      <p>How calorie deficits work, how large a deficit is safe, and how to set a realistic calorie target for steady weight loss.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n    <!-- Nutrition -->\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../high-protein-foods.html\" data-tag=\"Nutrition\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">🥩</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">Nutrition</div></div></div>\n      <h2>High Protein Foods List</h2>\n      <p>A comprehensive list of the best dietary protein sources ranked by protein content per 100 g, with serving suggestions.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n    <!-- Hydration -->\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../how-much-water-per-day.html\" data-tag=\"Hydration\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">💧</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">Hydration</div></div></div>\n      <h2>How Much Water Per Day?</h2>\n      <p>Daily water intake recommendations based on body weight, activity, and climate — plus signs of dehydration to watch for.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n    <!-- Exercise -->\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../best-exercises-to-lose-weight.html\" data-tag=\"Exercise\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">🏃</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">Exercise</div></div></div>\n      <h2>Best Exercises to Lose Weight</h2>\n      <p>The most effective exercise types for weight loss ranked by calorie burn, accessibility, and long-term adherence.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../how-to-lose-belly-fat.html\" data-tag=\"Exercise\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">💪</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">Exercise</div></div></div>\n      <h2>How to Lose Belly Fat</h2>\n      <p>Evidence-based strategies for reducing visceral and subcutaneous abdominal fat — including what actually works and what doesn't.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n    <!-- By Height -->\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../healthy-weight-160cm-female.html\" data-tag=\"By Height\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">📏</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">By Height</div></div></div>\n      <h2>Healthy Weight: 160 cm Women</h2>\n      <p>Healthy weight range, calorie needs, and height-specific health tips for women at 160 cm.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../healthy-weight-165cm-female.html\" data-tag=\"By Height\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">📏</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">By Height</div></div></div>\n      <h2>Healthy Weight: 165 cm Women</h2>\n      <p>Healthy weight range, calorie needs, and height-specific health tips for women at 165 cm.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../healthy-weight-170cm-female.html\" data-tag=\"By Height\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">📏</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">By Height</div></div></div>\n      <h2>Healthy Weight: 170 cm Women</h2>\n      <p>Healthy weight range, calorie needs, and height-specific health tips for women at 170 cm.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../healthy-weight-170cm-male.html\" data-tag=\"By Height\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">📏</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">By Height</div></div></div>\n      <h2>Healthy Weight: 170 cm Men</h2>\n      <p>Healthy weight range, calorie needs, and height-specific health tips for men at 170 cm.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../healthy-weight-175cm-male.html\" data-tag=\"By Height\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">📏</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">By Height</div></div></div>\n      <h2>Healthy Weight: 175 cm Men</h2>\n      <p>Healthy weight range, calorie needs, and height-specific health tips for men at 175 cm.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../healthy-weight-5ft4in-female.html\" data-tag=\"By Height\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">📏</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">By Height</div></div></div>\n      <h2>Healthy Weight: 5'4\" Women</h2>\n      <p>Healthy weight range, calorie needs, and height-specific health tips for women at 5 feet 4 inches.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../healthy-weight-5ft9in-male.html\" data-tag=\"By Height\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">📏</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">By Height</div></div></div>\n      <h2>Healthy Weight: 5'9\" Men</h2>\n      <p>Healthy weight range, calorie needs, and height-specific health tips for men at 5 feet 9 inches.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../healthy-weight-5ft6in-female.html\" data-tag=\"By Height\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">📏</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">By Height</div></div></div>\n      <h2>Healthy Weight: 5'6\" Women</h2>\n      <p>Healthy weight range, calorie needs, and height-specific health tips for women at 5 feet 6 inches.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n    <!-- By Age -->\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../healthy-bmi-20-year-old-female.html\" data-tag=\"By Age\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">🗓️</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">By Age</div></div></div>\n      <h2>Healthy BMI: Age 20 (Women)</h2>\n      <p>Body composition, muscle mass, and key health considerations for women in their 20s.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../healthy-bmi-30-year-old-female.html\" data-tag=\"By Age\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">🗓️</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">By Age</div></div></div>\n      <h2>Healthy BMI: Age 30 (Women)</h2>\n      <p>How body composition changes in your 30s and what to prioritise to maintain a healthy BMI.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../healthy-bmi-40-year-old-female.html\" data-tag=\"By Age\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">🗓️</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">By Age</div></div></div>\n      <h2>Healthy BMI: Age 40 (Women)</h2>\n      <p>Perimenopause, body recomposition, and evidence-based strategies for women in their 40s.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../healthy-bmi-50-year-old-female.html\" data-tag=\"By Age\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">🗓️</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">By Age</div></div></div>\n      <h2>Healthy BMI: Age 50 (Women)</h2>\n      <p>Post-menopause, metabolic changes, and evidence-based strategies for women in their 50s.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../healthy-bmi-30-year-old-male.html\" data-tag=\"By Age\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">🗓️</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">By Age</div></div></div>\n      <h2>Healthy BMI: Age 30 (Men)</h2>\n      <p>Metabolic slowdown, muscle preservation, and cardiovascular risk for men entering their 30s.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../healthy-bmi-40-year-old-male.html\" data-tag=\"By Age\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">🗓️</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">By Age</div></div></div>\n      <h2>Healthy BMI: Age 40 (Men)</h2>\n      <p>Testosterone decline, visceral fat risk, and the most impactful habits for men in their 40s.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../healthy-bmi-50-year-old-male.html\" data-tag=\"By Age\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">🗓️</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">By Age</div></div></div>\n      <h2>Healthy BMI: Age 50 (Men)</h2>\n      <p>Sarcopenia, andropause, and evidence-based strategies for maintaining a healthy BMI after 50.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n    <!-- New Articles -->\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../bmi-vs-body-fat.html\" data-tag=\"BMI\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">⚖️</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">BMI</div></div></div>\n      <h2>BMI vs Body Fat Percentage</h2>\n      <p>Which metric matters more for your health? When BMI misleads, when body fat % is essential, and how to use both together.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../healthy-bmi-asian-women.html\" data-tag=\"BMI\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">🌏</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">BMI</div></div></div>\n      <h2>Healthy BMI for Asian Women</h2>\n      <p>Why standard BMI ranges don't apply to Asian women, what thresholds to use instead, and what the research says.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../how-to-lose-5kg.html\" data-tag=\"Calories\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">📉</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">Calories</div></div></div>\n      <h2>How to Lose 5kg Safely</h2>\n      <p>A realistic, science-based plan — the right calorie deficit, protein targets, exercise approach, and timeline to expect.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n  \n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../bmi-calculator-not-accurate.html\" data-tag=\"BMI\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">🔬</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">BMI</div></div></div>\n      <h2>Is BMI Accurate?</h2>\n      <p>BMI has real limitations — muscle vs fat, ethnicity gaps, age effects. Here's when it works and when to use other metrics instead.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n  \n    <!-- Nutrition additions -->\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../what-to-eat-to-lose-weight.html\" data-tag=\"Nutrition\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">🥗</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">Nutrition</div></div></div>\n      <h2>What to Eat to Lose Weight</h2>\n      <p>No fad diets. The evidence-based foods that make a calorie deficit easier — what to eat more of, what to limit, and why.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../intermittent-fasting.html\" data-tag=\"Nutrition\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">⏱️</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">Nutrition</div></div></div>\n      <h2>Intermittent Fasting: Does It Work?</h2>\n      <p>An honest look at what the research actually shows — who IF works for, who should be cautious, and the most common mistakes.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n    <!-- Exercise additions -->\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../how-many-steps-per-day.html\" data-tag=\"Exercise\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">👟</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">Exercise</div></div></div>\n      <h2>How Many Steps Per Day Is Healthy?</h2>\n      <p>Is 10,000 steps backed by science? What the research actually shows about daily step count and realistic targets for different goals.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../cardio-vs-weights.html\" data-tag=\"Exercise\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">🏋️</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">Exercise</div></div></div>\n      <h2>Cardio vs Weight Training for Fat Loss</h2>\n      <p>Cardio burns more calories per session. Weights build muscle that burns calories at rest. Which actually wins — and why the answer might surprise you.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n    <!-- Hydration additions -->\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../signs-of-dehydration.html\" data-tag=\"Hydration\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">🚰</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">Hydration</div></div></div>\n      <h2>Signs of Dehydration</h2>\n      <p>Dehydration affects you before you feel thirsty. Learn the early warning signs, who's most at risk, and the urine colour test.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../does-water-help-lose-weight.html\" data-tag=\"Hydration\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">💧</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">Hydration</div></div></div>\n      <h2>Does Water Help You Lose Weight?</h2>\n      <p>Water doesn't burn fat directly — but it supports weight loss through three well-documented mechanisms. Here's what the research shows.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n\n  \n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../weight-loss-plateau.html\" data-tag=\"Calories\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">📈</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">Weight Loss</div></div></div>\n      <h2>Why You've Hit a Weight Loss Plateau</h2>\n      <p>Why plateaus happen, the physiology behind them, and exactly how to break through one.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../sleep-and-weight-loss.html\" data-tag=\"Calories\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">😴</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">Weight Loss</div></div></div>\n      <h2>How Sleep Affects Weight Loss</h2>\n      <p>Poor sleep sabotages fat loss through hormones and metabolism. How much sleep you need for results.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../stress-and-weight-gain.html\" data-tag=\"Calories\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">😤</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">Weight Loss</div></div></div>\n      <h2>Stress and Weight Gain: The Cortisol Connection</h2>\n      <p>Chronic stress raises cortisol, promotes visceral fat, and sabotages weight loss. The science and fixes.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../metabolism-facts.html\" data-tag=\"Calories\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">⚡</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">Weight Loss</div></div></div>\n      <h2>Metabolism: Facts, Myths & How to Boost It</h2>\n      <p>What metabolism actually is, what the myths get wrong, and what genuinely raises your metabolic rate.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../protein-for-weight-loss.html\" data-tag=\"Nutrition\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">🥩</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">Nutrition</div></div></div>\n      <h2>How Much Protein Do You Need to Lose Weight?</h2>\n      <p>Protein is the most important macronutrient for fat loss. Exactly how much you need and the best sources.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../how-long-to-lose-10kg.html\" data-tag=\"Calories\">\n      <div class=\"card-top\"><div class=\"card-icon\">🎯</div><div><div class=\"card-tag\">Weight Loss</div></div></div>\n      <h2>How Long Does It Take to Lose 10kg?</h2>\n      <p>The realistic timeline, how to set your calorie deficit, and month-by-month expectations.</p>\n      <div class=\"card-arrow\">Read guide →</div>\n    </a>\n    <a class=\"guide-card\" href=\"../best-diet-for-weight-loss.html\" data-tag=\"Calories\">\n 